{"rightSidebarLinks":[{"id":"model","title":"model (Template Driven)","subLink":null},{"id":"example","title":"Example","subLink":[]},{"id":"elementclass","title":"elementClass","subLink":[]},{"id":"error","title":"error","subLink":[]},{"id":"excludepropertiesdynamically","title":"Exclude properties dynamically","subLink":[]},{"id":"githubissues","title":"@model Github Issues","subLink":null}],"title":"@model","description":"","validatorType":"template-driven","validationTypeTitle":"Template Driven","type":"decorators","gitDocPath":"https://github.com/rxweb/rxweb.io/edit/master/docs/angular/reactive-forms/reactive-form-validators/decorators/model.md","category":"decorators","subCategory":null,"linkTitle":"model","tabArray":{},"innerHtml":null,"htmlContent":"<div class=\"title-bar top_title\"><p>@model</p></div> <div class=\"title-bar\"><p>This is helpfull where your same validation as well as showing error messages conditionally.</p></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'example'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>Example<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/decorators/model/template-driven/directives#example'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >let's create a user model and define a property of password in the model.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"model-add-model\"></div> \r\n<p class='showHideElement' >You have to use RxFormBuilder service to create FormGroup in the component.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"model-add-component\"></div> \r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"model-add-html\"></div> \r\n<div component=\"app-example-runner\" ref-component=\"app-model-add\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'elementclass'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>elementClass<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/decorators/model/template-driven/directives#elementclass'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >When you want to apply elementClass conditionally on multiple properties .</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"model-element-model\"></div> \r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"model-element-component\"></div> \r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"model-element-html\"></div> \r\n<div component=\"app-example-runner\" ref-component=\"app-model-element\" title=\"element with model\" key=\"element\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'error'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>error<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/decorators/model/template-driven/directives#error'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >When you want to set error property on more than two properties than it will be easier to set the <span class='highlighted'>error</span> property in propsConfig of model decorator.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"model-error-model\"></div> \r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"model-error-component\"></div> \r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"model-error-html\"></div> \r\n<div component=\"app-example-runner\" ref-component=\"app-model-error\" title=\"error with model\" key=\"error\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'excludepropertiesdynamically'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>Exclude properties dynamically<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/decorators/model/template-driven/directives#excludepropertiesdynamically'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >When you have more than two properties than it will be easier to set the <span class='highlighted'>ignore</span> property in propsConfig of model decorator.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"model-exclude-model\"></div> \r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"model-exclude-component\"></div> \r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"model-exclude-html\"></div> \r\n<div component=\"app-example-runner\" ref-component=\"app-model-exclude\" title=\"exclude with model\" key=\"exclude\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class=\"row page-section\" id=\"githubissues\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12\">\r\n<h2>Github Issues<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/decorators/model/template-driven/decorators#githubissues' fragment='githubissues'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n<div component=\"app-github-issue\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div component=\"app-contribution\"></div>\r\n"}